Developers
----------

Releasing a new version:

* Update HISTORY file

  + git add HISTORY.rst

  + git commit -m "Changelog for upcoming release 0.1.1."

* bumpversion patch

* Run tests

  + tox

* Release on PyPI

  + python setup.py sdist bdist_wheel

  + twine upload dist/* -r pypi -u -p

* Update github

  + git push

  + git push --tags

